author: Danny Schwartz
title: Mick Jenkins Plans To Releases Two Projects This Year
text:
Home > Music > Mick Jenkins Plans To Releases Two Projects This Year Mick Jenkins Plans To Releases Two Projects This Year 1 0 Posted by Danny Schwartz , Mar 7, 2017 at 10:03am "My next album is fully in the works." 
Mick Jenkins took to Twitter yesterday afternoon to explain that "Pressed For Time," his new release with GoldLink, is not a sign of things to come but a clearing of the decks chugs along on his next project. 
"My next album is fully in the works," he wrote. "I know y'all want that hard shit. Ima give it to you." 
He followed that promise by dropping a minor bomb: "I have two projects coming in 2017 actually." 
He concluded the PSA by teasing an upcoming project by jSTOCK, a member of his rap collective Free Nation which "promotes creative thought without accepting narrow views imposed by the powers that be."
